  "description": "Once per turn, when you hit a target with a melee weapon attack or a ranged weapon attack using a thrown weapon, you can imbue the attack with an additional effect based on a chosen giant type. You can use this feat a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, regaining all uses on a long rest. The saving throw DC for these effects equals 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Strength or Constitution modifier.",
